nd":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"這、這也沒辦法吧……！\n他一直跟著我後面，\n而且雨又越下越大，怎麼可能把他放著不管！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"fes3-CH-part1-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"原來如此……也就是說，\n這個亂七八糟的客廳是……？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"fes3-CH-part1-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"唉……真是的\n自從帶這隻小貓回來之後，我真的快累死了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"fes3-CH-part1-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"因為他很冷的樣子所以我想說幫他沖個熱水澡，\n結果他卻因為不想沖澡抓我的手臂……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"fes3-CH-part1-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"不僅如此，因為他還一身溼答答地在家裡亂跑，\n害得我得拿著毛巾到處追他……\n真是只靠外觀無法想像的Unstoppable……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"fes3-CH-part1-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"不過，在我用浴巾幫他擦乾身體的時候，\n他就這麼躺在我的大腿上睡著了……\n打滾跟發出呼嚕聲好一陣子……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"fes3-CH-part1-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"哈啊～～，小貓咪跟CHU²大人都可愛過頭了～～！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"shame02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"fes3-CH-part1-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"該不會，CHU²今後也打算\n繼續照顧這隻小貓咪嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"fes3-CH-part1-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceId